transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ji sir, ab aa gaya.
Customer: Aa gaya sir WhatsApp pe?
Executive: Haan, high ka message. Try kijiyega. Haan, high ka aayega saath mein ek link aayi hogi. Aap usko mujhe revert high kijiye ek baar.
Customer: Ye khul nahi raha lekin.
Executive: Wahi main bol raha tha aapse. Aap mujhe dobara se ek high kijiye.
Customer: Jai Shri Ram ka message bhej diya maine.
Executive: Theek hai, aa gaya. Ab main aapko dobara se send kar raha hu. Aap line pe rahiyega.
Executive: Ab ek baar kholiye sir.
Customer: Haan, khol raha hu.
Executive: Ab khul jayega.
(silence)
[unintelligible]
